snippet.title: Elon Musk Dumps Amber Heard | Daily Celebrity News | Splash TV
snippet.description:
Elon Musk and Amber Heard have called it quits for the second time and rumor has it he pulled the plug.

SUBSCRIBE NOW : https://goo.gl/JaLP0U

Well, that was fun while it lasted.

Yep, Elon Musk and Amber Heard have gone their separate ways.  Again.

The couple had just rekindled their romance only weeks before and now it's being reported that their relationship fizzled out.

The pair was recently spotted enjoying a sushi date in Los Angeles, and there were rumors that things were going well.

But all good things must come to an end, right.

Elon and Amber first started dating back in 2016, and when they broke up the first time it was her that pulled the plug.  But rumor has it this time around he called it quits.

Still no word on what exactly caused the rift in their relationship, but maybe we shouldn't hold our breath that they'll ever get back together again.

The good news is they're both still very hot commodities and should have no trouble getting back on their feet.
